00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:03,360
- Bagus. Bagaimana cara kerjanya?
- Itu sifon.

9
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,200
Saat cairan...

10
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:09,720
Bergerak melawan gravitasi,
karena tekanan...

11
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,680
- Kau tak tahu.
- Aku tahu itu bisa bekerja.

12
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,520
Jangan berkeliaran.

