92
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:11,280
Saudaramu berada di Wyoming mana?

93
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:14,560
Kontak terakhir datang
dari menara radio di dekat Cody.

94
00:12:14,640 --> 00:12:15,920
Cody.

95
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,160
Cody.

96
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:20,160
- Cody. Astaga, itu jauh di dalam.
- Ya.

