141
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:38,720
Aku gigih.

142
00:14:41,640 --> 00:14:43,600
Kau bangun pagi.
Jika kau ingin tidur lagi...

143
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:45,080
Aku bahkan tidak lelah.

144
00:15:17,760 --> 00:15:18,760
Tetap di sini.

145
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:05,160
<i>Selatan Wichita</i>

146
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:07,120
<i>Utara Des Moines</i>

